  "texts": [
    "We can divide these datasets into CTDGs and DTDGs, according to the collection and storage methods of the datasets.",
    "However, with appropriate processing, they can be transformed into one another.",
    "From these datasets, we can observe the following characteristics:• Domains and applications.",
    "These datasets cover a diverse range of domains, including social, music, political, transportation, economic, and e-commerce networks.",
    "This diversity enables researchers to test and validate algorithms on various real-world applications.• Scale."
  ]
}